{"tid":2175046,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"議辦外持刀毀文宣揚言「淋漒水」 七旬老翁認罪判監13星期","createTime":"2020-08-26T09:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T09:35:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd13ce6ca496d029466e750041a5b860e373524d","tid":2175046,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/GZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FGZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatj1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=4092ee5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FGZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y%2F&h=8de9be65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/GZE5VSXC2NEOTI5QUPT5GTME2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n退休七旬老翁疑因政見問題，兩個月前用黑筆塗污張貼於區議員辦事處外的連儂牆文宣。議員在議辦外張貼老翁容貌，老翁不滿，持刀踩場並威脅議員助理指「信唔信我真係用刀桶你」，更揚言「淋漒水」。老翁事後被捕，今在屯門裁判法院承認刑事毀壞及刑事恐嚇共四罪，辯方求情欲索取感化報告，惟署理主任裁判官張潔宜指，被告持刀犯案，明顯有預謀而非一時衝動，判他入獄13星期。"},{"pid":"7b84bd2a9b0eba6b07157769ee2309f900fb10d8","tid":2175046,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015f72b1bc68eb6b8600cac69439be1738d359bd","tid":2175046,"uid":126782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acf0b81fcc78b9f6bac58c0946268835e42d75f","tid":2175046,"uid":14983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"持刀但冇用黎斬人<br />\n高尚情操喎"},